    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Documents outlining a proposed journey. Originally, a list of destinations in the Roman Empire with the distances between them, thought to be measured from the 'Millarium Aureum' or 'Golden Milestone' in the Roman Forum.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
